    "text": "# April 20, 2026  \nMonday again. The weekend went too fast. Back to the daily routine.  \nMorning rush as usual. Dropped Neetish at school. She's been quiet lately. Might be the exam pressure. Need to talk to her tonight.  \nOffice was chaotic. The new project has some technical issues. Spent the whole day solving them. Had to skip lunch. By evening, everyone was tired but we managed to fix the critical problems.  \nPreeti picked up the kids. She mentioned that Neetish didn't eat her tiffin properly at school. Will check what's going on with her.  \nMohan has been fighting with his friend Aryan again. This is becoming a regular thing. Need to have a conversation with him.  \nEvening walk with Browny. He's getting better at not pulling the leash. Proud of him.  \nPreeti made order from Swad (our favorite Indore restaurant). Ordered dal makhani and naan. The kids were happy.  \nHelped Neetish with her project before sleep. She seems more relaxed now.",
